headline.main: The Route between San Francisco and China.

docs.lead_paragraph: SIR: I have the honor to inform the Department of the arrival of the Fenimore Cooper at this port after a cruise of forty-three days; during which we visited the positions assigned several dangers between San Francisco and the Sandwich Islands, on and near the jome to China, as registered on the Chart of Reported Dangers, compiled under the direction of Commander RODGERS, viz.:
